FBIS4-30370 "dreas123_n_94010" FBIS-EAS-94-123 Daily Report 25 Jun 1994 Vietnam Defense Ministry Confers Orders on Generals Defense Ministry Confers Orders on Generals BK2706090094 Hanoi Voice of Vietnam Network in Vietnamese 2300 GMT 25 Jun 94 BK2706090094 Hanoi Voice of Vietnam Network Vietnamese BFN [Text] Authorized by the president of the Socialist Republic of Vietnam, the Ministry of National Defense yesterday, 25 June, held in Hanoi a solemn ceremoney to confer the Ho Chi Minh Order on Lieutenant General Le Tu Dong and Lieutenant General Dang Kinh, aka Le Trung Truc; and the Independence Order first class on Lieutenant General Le Linh and Lieutenant General Do Quoc Tuan. The orders were awarded for their valuable contributions to the protection and construction of the fatherland.
